OL,3,CJeremy Hunt says pensions triple lock
OL,4,Cwill be in next Tory manifesto
OL,6,Fhas pledged the triple lock for will
OL,7,Fbe included in the Tory election
OL,8,Fmanifesto, calling the commitment
OL,9,F"very important".
OL,11,FThe chancellor said the safeguard
OL,12,Fwould be kept throughout the next
OL,13,Fparliament under the Conservatives,
OL,14,Finsisting he was confident the
OL,15,F"expensive" policy could be paid for
OL,16,Fthrough economic growth.
OL,18,FThe triple lock refers to the
OL,19,Fcommitment to raise the state pension
OL,20,Fevery year by wage growth, inflation
OL,21,For 2.5%, whichever is highest.
