OL,6,FElsewhere, Mr Hunt refused to commit
OL,7,Fto compensation for so-called Waspi
OL,8,Fwomen - who were hit by changes to
OL,9,Fstate pension eligibility in the 1950s.
OL,11,FThe government has been accused of
OL,12,Ffailing to to adequately inform those
OL,13,Fborn in that period about an increase
OL,14,Fin the entitlement age.
OL,16,FSpeaking to broadcasters, Mr Hunt
OL,17,Fdenied pushing the decision to the
OL,18,Fright for a future administration to
OL,19,Fdeal, as Labour enjoys a sustained
OL,20,Fdouble-digit lead in opinion polls
OL,21,Fahead of this year's election.
