OL,6,FHe said the issue highlighted by the
OL,7,FWomen Against State Pension Inequality
OL,8,F(Waspi) campaign was "genuinely more
OL,9,Fcomplicated" than others in which
OL,10,Fcompensation has been promised, like
OL,11,Fthe infected blood disaster and the
OL,12,FPost Office Horizon scandal.
OL,14,FThe development comes after a long-
OL,15,Fawaited report by the Parliamentary
OL,16,Fand Health Service Ombudsman (PHSO)
OL,17,Fthat found the and those affected
OL,18,Fshould receive an apology and
OL,19,Fcompensation.
