OL,6,FAsked whether it was responsible for
OL,7,Fthe government to leave "huge unpaid
OL,8,Fbills" to the next parliament, he
OL,9,Fsaid: "We had the ombudsman's report
OL,10,Fon Thursday, but we've also had a
OL,11,Freport from the High Court and Court
OL,12,Fof Appeal in 2020 that says the
OL,13,FDepartment for Work and Pensions (DWP)
OL,14,Fbehaved completely within the law and
OL,15,Fdidn't discriminate.
OL,17,F"So, it appears to say something
OL,18,Fdifferent and we do need to get to the
OL,19,Fbottom of that apparent difference
OL,20,Fbetween the two."
