OL,6,FHe added: "We want to resolve it as
OL,7,Fquickly as we can, but there's no
OL,8,Fsecret vault of money.
OL,10,F"The money we would pay in
OL,11,Fcompensation has to come from other
OL,12,Ftaxpayers, so we do have to take time
OL,13,Fto get this fair."
OL,15,FCampaigners have demanded action over
OL,16,Fthe report, warning Prime Minister
OL,17,FRishi Sunak will be on a "sticky
OL,18,Fwicket" seeking votes from Waspi women
OL,19,Fwhen he goes to the country later this
OL,20,Fyear, if he does not heed the
OL,21,Fombudsman's findings.
